tabs.tab_title: What types of car wash services do you provide?
tabs.tab_content: We offer a variety of car wash services including basic exterior washes, full-service washes, interior detailing, waxing, and tire cleaning. We also have premium packages that combine multiple services for a comprehensive clean.

tabs.tab_title: Do you offer eco-friendly car wash options?
tabs.tab_content: Yes, we offer eco-friendly car wash services using biodegradable soaps and water-saving techniques to minimize our environmental impact.

tabs.tab_title: Do you have any membership or loyalty programs?
tabs.tab_content: Yes, we offer a membership program that includes unlimited basic washes for a monthly fee, as well as a loyalty program where you earn points for each wash that can be redeemed for discounts and free services.

tabs.tab_title: Do I need to make an appointment for a car wash?
tabs.tab_content: While appointments are not required for basic car washes, we recommend scheduling an appointment for detailing services to ensure availability and reduce wait times.

tabs.tab_title: Is my vehicle safe during the wash process?
tabs.tab_content: Yes, we take great care to ensure the safety of your vehicle. Our equipment is regularly maintained, and our staff is trained to handle all vehicles with care.

tabs.tab_title: Are you insured in case of damage to my car?
tabs.tab_content: Yes, we are fully insured. In the unlikely event of damage, we will work with you to resolve the issue promptly and fairly.

tabs.tab_title: Can you handle special requests or custom detailing?
tabs.tab_content: Yes - from strategy development to content creation to monitoring and reporting, we offer a comprehensive social media marketing service.

tabs.tab_title: How do you ensure the quality of your car wash services?
tabs.tab_content: Our team is trained to follow strict quality control protocols. We use top-quality products and equipment, and we perform regular inspections to maintain high standards.
